Title: Anonymous
Plot: 3 months after the murder of a man, in a scene staged to look like a suicide, another similar murder occurs. Warrick and Nick investigate the case of a man who drove over a cliff and is now unconscious.
ParentalRatingReason: Violence, sexual themes and content that may disturb
